llite_stats_write_bytes.samples_sum: total size of all llite layer write IOs

ost_read_rpc_bytes_data.sample_min: minimum size of OSC layer read RPCs
ost_read_rpc_bytes_data.sample_max: maximum size of OSC layer read RPCs
ost_read_rpc_bytes_data.samples_sum: total size of all OSC layer read RPCs

cur_dirty_bytes: current amount of dirty pages (in bytes) in dirty page cache
cur_grant_bytes: current amount of space the client has reserved for the writeback cache with each OST
cur_read_rif: current amount of read RPCs in air
pending_read_pages: pending amount of read pages waiting to be cached
cur_write_rif: current amount of write RPCs in air
pending_write_pages: pending amount of write pages waiting to be cached
is_dist_centered: is pages_per_rpc distribution centered: Centered(+1), Decentered(-1), Empty(0)
avg_pages_per_write_rpc: average pages observed among issued write RPCs
write_avg_xfer_speed: average transfer speed of write RPCs
write_max_xfer_speed: maximum transfer speed of write RPCs
used_pct_dirty_cache: percentages of dirty page cache that is occupied
avg_waittime: average of waittime for all completed RPCs
write_rpc_generation_rate: how fast data is being utilized to generate RPCs
avg_write_rpc_latency_per_unit_data: the average amount of latency observed during write RPC communication for a unit (in Page, size = 4kB) of data
avg_write_rpc_waittime: average of waittime for completed write RPCs
avg_rpcs_in_flight: average number of observed RPCs in flight
